  "comment": {
    "text": "This is the body text of a confirmation dialog that appears when a user attempts to delete their DocSpace portal. It informs the user that the deletion is permanent and that a request will be sent to the owner's email. The variables `{{domain}}`, `{{productName}}`, and `{{email}}` represent the portal's domain, the product name, and the owner's email address, respectively.",
